2. The most popular issue categories are ranked correctly based on complaint volume. \b Pass\b0\par
3. The popularity widget shows the correct count for the selected time period. \b Pass\b0\par
4. A newly added grievance appears in the popularity data after refresh. \b Pass\b0\par
5. Repeated complaints for the same issue increase the popularity score as expected. \b Fail\b0\par
6. The popularity view filters out irrelevant or archived grievances. \b Fail\b0\par
7. Switching between 3M, 6M, 12M, and All views changes the popularity trend correctly. \b Fail\b0\par
8. The popularity section reflects real-time updates when new complaints are submitted. \b Pass\b0\par
